@Deprecated
public class JavaProgram
extends AbstractSimpleRule<JavaProgram>

Tablesaw plugin for creating/compiling a java program. This plugin acts as a wrapper for the rules to create a java program from building class files to packaging a jar. Use tablesaw.addons.java.JavaProgram instead.
